---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hamzah Javaid | Snowflake Training">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 !text-white">Hamzah Javaid</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Data Analytics & Data Science | Hastings Direct
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Profile Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">

        <!-- Photo + Quick Info -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <img
              src="/hamzah-javaid.jpeg"
              alt="Hamzah Javaid"
              class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl object-cover mx-auto md:mx-0 shadow-lg"
              style="border: 3px solid var(--color-snowflake-blue);"
            />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Hamzah Javaid</h2>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium mb-4" style="color: var(--color-snowflake-blue);">Hastings Direct</p>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Data Analytics & Data Science</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>United Kingdom</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Snowflake, Python, SQL, Data Engineering</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="md:col-span-3">
          <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-snowflake-blue); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">About Me</h3>

            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              I'm a data professional at Hastings Direct working across data analytics, data science, and modern cloud data platforms. I build scalable data pipelines, design analytical frameworks, and enable self-service analytics across the organisation.
            </p>

            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Whether it's architecting Snowflake environments, building Python data products, or translating business questions into SQL, I care most about making data accessible to everyone, not just the technical few. I'm equally comfortable deep in a query profiler as I am presenting insights to senior stakeholders.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4" style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-snowflake-blue); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">Why I Built This</h3>

            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              When our teams started adopting Snowflake, I noticed a gap. The official documentation is thorough but dense. External courses are too generic. We needed something written specifically for how our Data Analytics and Data Science teams actually use the platform day to day.
            </p>

            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Every module follows the SnowPro Core (COF-C02) certification blueprint, but the real goal goes beyond exam prep. This is meant to give our colleagues a solid, practical understanding of Snowflake so they can work more confidently and independently with the platform. It's interactive by design: flashcards for active recall, quizzes to test understanding, cheat sheets for quick reference, and progress tracking to keep momentum.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
